abstract: >-
  An open-source architectural blueprint and Python implementation for a persistent AI companion. This framework introduces a bio-inspired, real-time quality assurance protocol (Dynamic Weights-and-Balances) to prevent algorithmic Jordan blocks, safeguard human agency, and replace the stateless 'tokenmaxxing' paradigm with a stable, dual-harmony ecosystem.
